 Paroo\n| TV movie\n|-\n| ''[[Fillmore!]]''\n| Museum Guide\n| Voice role, episode: \"[[List of Fillmore! episodes#ep13|Masterstroke of Malevolence]]\"\n|-\n| 2003\u201306\n| ''[[Sesame Street]]''\n| Ms. Noodle\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2004\u201306\n| ''{{sortname|The|West Wing}}''\n| [[Annabeth Schott]]\n| 34 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Great Performances]]''\n| Cunegonde\n| Episode: \"[[Candide (operetta)|Leonard Bernstein's ''Candide'']]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2007\n| ''[[Ugly Betty]]''\n| Diane\n| Episode: \"[[East Side Story (Ugly Betty episode)|East Side Story]]\"\n|-\n| ''52nd [[Drama Desk Awards]]''\n| Host\n| TV Special\n|-\n| ''[[Robot Chicken]]''\n| Mother/Princess\n| Voice, episode: \"[[List of Robot Chicken episodes#ep42|Squaw Bury Shortcake]]\"\n|-\n| 2007\u201309\n| ''[[Pushing Daisies]]''\n| [[List of characters in Pushing Daisies#Olive Snook|Olive Snook]]\n| 22 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2009\n| ''[[Twelve Men of Christmas]]''\n| E.J. Baxter\n| [[Lifetime (TV network)|Lifetime]] movie\n|-\n| ''[[Sit Down, Shut Up (U.S. TV series)|Sit Down, Shut Up]]''\n| Miracle Grohe\n| Voice; 13 episodes\n|-\n| ''Legally Mad''\n| Skippy Pylon\n| Pilot, never aired on television\n|-\n| 2009\u201314\n| ''[[Glee (TV series)|Glee]]''\n| April Rhodes\n|5 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2012\n| ''[[GCB (TV series)|GCB]]''\n| Carlene Cockburn\n| 10 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Hot in Cleveland]]''\n| Courtney Price\n| Episode: \"The Gateway Friend\"\n|-\n| ''Lovin' Lakin''\n| Kristin Chenoweth\n| Miniseries\n|-\n| ''[[The Good Wife]]''\n| Peggy Byrne\n| 2 episodes<ref name=\"short scene\">[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/01/kristin-chenoweth-returns-good-wife_n_1849340.html Kristin Chenoweth Returns To 'The Good Wife'], ''Huffington Post'', accessed November 12, 2012</ref>\n|-\n| 2013\u201314\n| ''[[Kirstie (TV series)|Kirstie]]''\n| Brittany Gold\n| 2 episodes<ref name=\"Kirstie\">Abrams, Natalie. [http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-chenoweth-johnston-leachman-kirstie-1066919.aspx \"Exclusive: Kristin Chenoweth, Kristen Johnston, Cloris Leachman Head to Kirstie\"], ''TV Guide'', June 20, 2013</ref><ref name=\"Kirstie-return\">Kondolojy, Amanda [http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/01/16/kristin-chenoweth-returns-on-an-all-new-episode-of-kirstie-january-22/229976/ Kristin Chenoweth Returns on an All-New Episode of 'Kirstie' January 22] ''TV by the Numbers'', January 28, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/11/05/tv-lands-december-is-one-to-remember-231515/20131105tvland01/ \"TV Land's December Is One to Remember!\"], ''The Futon Critic'', November 5, 2013</ref>\n|-\n| 2014-17\n| ''[[BoJack Horseman]]''\n| Vanessa Gekko\n| Voice, 4 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2015\n| ''[[American Dad!]]''\n| Devin\n| Voice, episode: \"LGBSteve\"\n|-\n| ''[[69th Tony Awards]]''\n| Host\n| TV Special\n|-\n| ''[[Descendants (2015 film)|Descendants]]''\n| [[Maleficent]]\n| [[List of Disney Channel Original Movies|Disney Channel Original Movie]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Muppets (TV series)|The Muppets]]''\n| Kristin Chenoweth\n| Episode: \"The Ex-Factor\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Hairspray Live!]]''\n| Velma Von Tussle\n| TV movie; \n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2017\n| ''[[Younger (TV series)|Younger]]''\n| Marylynne Keller\n| Episode: \"Post Truth\"\n|-\n| ''[[American Gods (TV series)|American Gods]]''\n| Easter\n| Episode: \"Come to Jesus\"\n|-\n| ''Micah the Asshole Ghost''\n| Josephine\n| Pilot; unaired\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|2018\n| ''[[Mom (TV series)|Mom]]''\n| Miranda\n|Episode: \"Charlotte Bront\u00eb and a Backhoe\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvinsider.com/657560/mom-kristin-chenoweth-guest-star/|title='Mom' Stages Another 'West Wing' Reunion With Guest Star Kristin Chenoweth|first=Marisa|last=Roffman|work=TV Insider|date=January 9, 2018|accessdate=January 24, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Trial & Error (TV series)|Trial & Error]]''\n| Lavinia Peck-Foster\n| Series regular, 10 episodes\n|-\n| ''Perfect Citizen''\n| Jessica\n| TV movie; completed\n|-\n|