{"title_page": "1994\u201395 A Lyga", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n|season           = 1994\u201395\n|dates            = \n|competition      = [[A Lyga]]\n|winners          = <!-- (th title) -->\n|relegated        = \n|continentalcup1  = \n|continentalcup1 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup2  = \n|continentalcup2 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup3  = \n|continentalcup3 qualifiers = \n|league topscorer = \n|biggest home win = \n|biggest away win = \n|highest scoring  = \n|matches          = \n|total goals      = \n|prevseason = [[1993\u201394 A Lyga|1993\u201394]]\n|nextseason = [[1995\u201396 A Lyga|1995\u201396]]\n|updated    = \n}}\nStatistics of the [[A Lyga]] for the 1994\u201395 season.\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 12 teams, and [[Inkaras-Grifas Kaunas]] won the championship.\n\n==Final table==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=INK|name_INK=[[FK Inkaras Kaunas|Inkaras-Grifas]]\n|team2=FK\u017d|name_FK\u017d=[[FK \u017dalgiris|\u017dalgiris]]\n|team3=ROM|name_ROM=[[ROMAR Ma\u017eeikiai|ROMAR]]\n|team4=FKP|name_FKP=[[FK Panerys Vilnius|Panerys]]\n|team5=PSK|name_PSK=[[FK Atlantas|Aras]]\n|team6=FBK|name_FBK=[[FBK Kaunas]]\n|team7=SAK|name_SAK=[[FK Kareda Kaunas|Sakalas]]\n|team8=FKE|name_FKE=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]\n|team9=BAN|name_BAN=[[FK Banga Garg\u017edai|Banga]]\n|team10=FKU|name_FKU=[[FK Ukmerg\u0117|Ukmerg\u0117]]\n|team11=VLP|name_VLP=[[FK Sirijus Klaip\u0117da|Sirijus]]\n|team12=INT|name_INT=[[FK Interas Visaginas|Interas-AE]]\n|win_INK=16|draw_INK=4|loss_INK=2|gf_INK=50|ga_INK=12|status_INK=C\n|win_FK\u017d=17|draw_FK\u017d=2|loss_FK\u017d=3|gf_FK\u017d=61|ga_FK\u017d=14\n|win_ROM=15|draw_ROM=4|loss_ROM=3|gf_ROM=51|ga_ROM=14|status_ROM=R\n|win_FKP=11|draw_FKP=6|loss_FKP=5|gf_FKP=35|ga_FKP=25\n|win_PSK=13|draw_PSK=1|loss_PSK=8|gf_PSK=41|ga_PSK=28\n|win_FBK=8|draw_FBK=8|loss_FBK=6|gf_FBK=25|ga_FBK=22\n|win_SAK=9|draw_SAK=4|loss_SAK=9|gf_SAK=37|ga_SAK=23\n|win_FKE=7|draw_FKE=8|loss_FKE=7|g